Added capability statement cSnmpCommunityCapACSWV03R000 for Application Control Engine (ACE). Updated the conformance group name for cSnmpCommunityCapCatOSV06R0301 from snmpCommunityGroup to snmpCommunityTableGroup since the new version of SNMP-COMMUNITY-MIB (RFC3584) has changed the name to avoid conflicts with SNMPv2-MIB.
Initial version of this MIB module.
